<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Account Created</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            background: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome, {{f_name}} {{l_name}}!</h2>
        <p>Your account has been successfully created.</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
        <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> {{tempPassword}}</p>
        <p>Please log in and change your password as soon as possible.</p>
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Click here to log in</a>
        <p class="footer">Best regards,<br>The Team</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>